39
00:04:11.751 --> 00:04:12.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Tench] Big step.

40
00:04:14.295 --> 00:04:17.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-I knew she was it when I met her.
-How'd you know?

41
00:04:17.507 --> 00:04:20.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Uh, we saw things the same way.

42
00:04:21.302 --> 00:04:23.346 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Holden] And you're how old?
-Twenty-six.

43
00:04:24.055 --> 00:04:27.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You play sports in high school?
I'm guessing not the football team.

44
00:04:28.184 --> 00:04:29.978 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Band? Debate?
-No.

45
00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:31.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Then what did you do?

46
00:04:32.647 --> 00:04:35.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Uh, I... nothing.

47
00:04:38.695 --> 00:04:41.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, you're doing good now.
Got your own place and everything.

48
00:04:42.532 --> 00:04:44.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Got this place for Beverly Jean.

49
00:04:44.701 --> 00:04:46.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
