52
00:04:52.125 --> 00:04:54.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
A few blocks over on Chestnut.

53
00:04:54.210 --> 00:04:56.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-With your family?
-Uh, with my mom.

54
00:04:56.421 --> 00:04:59.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It must have been hard on her,
seeing you leave home.

55
00:04:59.382 --> 00:05:02.468 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I think she was happy to see me move on.

56
00:05:03.886 --> 00:05:07.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
She loved Beverly Jean as much as I did.

57
00:05:07.265 --> 00:05:10.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Mrs. Barnwright goes to my church, too.
First United Methodist.

58
00:05:11.519 --> 00:05:13.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So you two know each other from church?

59
00:05:13.229 --> 00:05:15.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah. You and Rose.

60
00:05:15.106 --> 00:05:18.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Mostly by sight now.
I don't go much anymore.

61
00:05:19.319 --> 00:05:22.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Was your mother a disciplinarian?

62
00:05:22.697 --> 00:05:24.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You mean strict?

63
00:05:24.324 --> 00:05:27.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Holden] Yeah. She crack the whip?

64
00:05:27.160 --> 00:05:28.828 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Uh...

65
00:05:28.911 --> 00:05:30.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
She just cried.

66
00:05:30.830 --> 00:05:33.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, I'm sure it was difficult
raising two kids without a dad.

67
00:05:33.666 --> 00:05:35.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, he split when I was ten.

68
00:05:35.960 --> 00:05:38.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-What was your father like?
-I don't much remember him.

69
00:05:39.839 --> 00:05:41.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You and Beverly Jean ever fight?

70
00:05:43.009 --> 00:05:44.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Perfectly normal for a young couple.

71
00:05:46.763 --> 00:05:48.056 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sometimes.

72
00:05:48.723 --> 00:05:49.849 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Tench] What'd you fight about?

73
00:05:50.433 --> 00:05:52.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Just stupid stuff.

74
00:05:52.518 --> 00:05:53.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Like what?

75
00:05:53.895 --> 00:05:55.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Like, uh...

76
00:05:56.189 --> 00:05:57.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
what movie to go to.

77
00:05:58.524 --> 00:06:00.985 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Tench] Any nerves around the engagement?
-No, sir.

78
00:06:02.320 --> 00:06:04.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You got this place for her?
Did she like it?

79
00:06:06.699 --> 00:06:07.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
She, uh...

80
00:06:09.744 --> 00:06:13.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She wanted to make it pretty
when she moved in.

81
00:06:13.331 --> 00:06:14.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Tench] When was that gonna be?

82
00:06:14.624 --> 00:06:16.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-After the wedding.
-Traditional, huh?

83
00:06:16.959 --> 00:06:19.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Yeah.
-[Holden] Was that for your mother?

84
00:06:19.462 --> 00:06:21.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That was just to keep it proper.

85
00:06:22.381 --> 00:06:24.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Was she saving herself for marriage?

86
00:06:26.761 --> 00:06:29.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well, maybe she didn't want to wait.

87
00:06:30.014 --> 00:06:32.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Girls like fooling around
just as much as boys.

88
00:06:33.726 --> 00:06:35.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That's okay, Benjamin.

89
00:06:35.978 --> 00:06:37.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We understand, that's...

90
00:06:38.064 --> 00:06:39.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
That's private.

91
00:06:39.524 --> 00:06:40.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We'll keep it private.

92
00:06:42.568 --> 00:06:44.237 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Benjamin] Uh, well...

93
00:06:45.863 --> 00:06:48.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Beverly Jean was, uh, my...

94
00:06:49.700 --> 00:06:50.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
first, uh...

95
00:06:51.452 --> 00:06:53.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Your first sexual experience?

96
00:06:53.871 --> 00:06:54.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah.

97
00:06:56.707 --> 00:06:57.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But she was nice.

98
00:06:59.919 --> 00:07:03.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I don't know what all this has to do
with what happened to her--

99
00:07:03.256 --> 00:07:06.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Listen, Benjamin.
We're from a particular unit of the FBI.

100
00:07:06.467 --> 00:07:09.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We investigate murders
when there's a sexual angle.

101
00:07:09.387 --> 00:07:11.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It may be unpleasant, but it's what we do.

102
00:07:14.642 --> 00:07:17.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[sobbing]

103
00:07:17.937 --> 00:07:19.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's awful, what was done to her.

104
00:07:20.982 --> 00:07:22.275 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Does he know?

105
00:07:23.901 --> 00:07:25.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Mark, seriously?

106
00:07:27.488 --> 00:07:30.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He only knows about the breasts.
It was another officer--

107
00:07:32.285 --> 00:07:35.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-It's hard keeping this quiet.
-I want to talk to Mrs. Barnwright.

108
00:07:35.204 --> 00:07:37.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Should we stop at a pay phone,
give her a heads up, too?

109
00:07:37.623 --> 00:07:39.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-That'd be fair.
-[Holden] What about the tears?

110
00:07:39.667 --> 00:07:41.294 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-I didn't buy them.
-Think he was faking?

111
00:07:41.377 --> 00:07:43.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Tench] Seemed a bit much.
-[Mark] Given what he's been through?

112
00:07:43.713 --> 00:07:46.632 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-It sure got us out of there.
-He's obviously a mama's boy.

113
00:07:46.716 --> 00:07:48.301 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Or he knows how to play one.

114
00:07:49.469 --> 00:07:50.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What do you mean?

115
00:07:50.720 --> 00:07:53.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He was a virgin? He serves donuts?

116
00:07:53.723 --> 00:07:57.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
All of that could have been rehearsed,
especially since he knew we were coming.

117
00:07:59.645 --> 00:08:02.231 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Benjamin has never seemed
like a performer to me.

118
00:08:03.483 --> 00:08:05.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Two Feds in your living room
would make anybody nervous.

119
00:08:05.610 --> 00:08:08.279 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Look at him, you think
he could have easily moved a body?

120
00:08:08.362 --> 00:08:10.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Not without bursting into tears.

121
00:08:10.281 --> 00:08:11.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[laughs]

122
00:08:15.786 --> 00:08:17.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[woman]<i> I always worried about Benjamin.</i>

123
00:08:17.955 --> 00:08:20.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Tench]<i> He was living with you</i>
<i>when he met Beverly Jean?</i>

124
00:08:20.708 --> 00:08:25.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-He was so excited to have a girlfriend.
-Did she reciprocate those feelings?

125
00:08:26.214 --> 00:08:28.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He said that she was crazy about him.

126
00:08:28.174 --> 00:08:30.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Did you meet her?
-Of course.

127
00:08:31.469 --> 00:08:32.762 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What were they like together?

128
00:08:32.845 --> 00:08:35.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well, they were... normal.

129
00:08:35.932 --> 00:08:39.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
She teased him a lot. He pretended
not to enjoy it, but I know he did.

130
00:08:40.770 --> 00:08:43.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Benjamin told us
the two of them argued sometimes.

131
00:08:44.941 --> 00:08:46.359 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Did you see him?

132
00:08:47.652 --> 00:08:48.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
This morning.

133
00:08:50.863 --> 00:08:52.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Is he in trouble?

134
00:08:53.574 --> 00:08:57.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We're just going over the case again,
talking to everyone who knew Beverly Jean.

135
00:08:58.329 --> 00:09:01.874 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well... I never heard them argue.

136
00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:06.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Benjamin is soft, you know.

137
00:09:06.254 --> 00:09:07.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What was he like as a kid?

138
00:09:07.797 --> 00:09:12.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He was always sensitive.
But when his father ran off, he just...

139
00:09:15.012 --> 00:09:16.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Holden] What do you mean?

140
00:09:17.932 --> 00:09:19.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Well...

141
00:09:19.725 --> 00:09:21.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
he started to cry a lot, wet the bed.

142
00:09:21.936 --> 00:09:24.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-He wouldn't leave the house.
-[Holden] That must have been difficult.

143
00:09:24.647 --> 00:09:27.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I had to leave the kids
on their own a lot.

144
00:09:27.733 --> 00:09:31.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Rose helped out,
but she was just so little.

145
00:09:33.990 --> 00:09:36.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Those were hard years.
I did a lot of praying.

146
00:09:38.995 --> 00:09:41.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But then Rose met Frank
