00:33:01.980 --> 00:33:03.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
or for him.

586
00:33:04.065 --> 00:33:07.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[baby cries]

587
00:33:24.544 --> 00:33:25.753 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What are we missing?

588
00:33:29.590 --> 00:33:31.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Did you see those bruises on her arm?
-[Tench] Yeah.

589
00:33:32.218 --> 00:33:33.302 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You think Frank did that?

590
00:33:33.386 --> 00:33:36.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Her mother told us that he wouldn't let
anyone else get close to her.

591
00:33:38.516 --> 00:33:39.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Should we search Frank's car?

592
00:33:40.476 --> 00:33:42.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-I would need a warrant.
-[Tench] Let's get one.

593
00:33:45.064 --> 00:33:48.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Mark. There's a young woman downstairs
asking for you.

594
00:33:59.620 --> 00:34:00.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hi, Rose.

595
00:34:06.544 --> 00:34:07.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[stammers] Do--
[clears throat]

596
00:34:10.590 --> 00:34:14.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[whispers] Do you promise my baby will
be okay if I tell you what happened?

597
00:34:15.136 --> 00:34:16.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Of course.

598
00:34:20.975 --> 00:34:21.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's okay.

599
00:34:23.770 --> 00:34:25.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-It's okay. Hey.
-[sobs]

600
00:34:33.946 --> 00:34:37.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So you said Frank was not home
the night Beverly Jean disappeared?

601
00:34:40.453 --> 00:34:41.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes.

602
00:34:42.080 --> 00:34:43.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Do you know where he was?

603
00:34:45.750 --> 00:34:46.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes.

604
00:34:48.419 --> 00:34:49.462 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Where was he?

605
00:34:50.588 --> 00:34:53.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Benji called us that night
and asked Frank to come over.

606
00:34:56.344 --> 00:34:57.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Okay.

607
00:34:58.930 --> 00:35:00.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So Frank left.

608
00:35:00.848 --> 00:35:02.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
How long was he gone?

609
00:35:06.646 --> 00:35:09.899 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He called after two or three hours.
Asked me to come over there too.

610
00:35:09.982 --> 00:35:12.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-What time was this?
-Ten or eleven?

611
00:35:12.985 --> 00:35:14.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But I told him I was tired.

612
00:35:15.696 --> 00:35:17.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
My back hurt. My feet.

613
00:35:19.992 --> 00:35:21.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I was more than eight months pregnant.

614
00:35:22.370 --> 00:35:24.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Did he say why
he wanted you to come over?

615
00:35:24.789 --> 00:35:25.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No.

616
00:35:27.291 --> 00:35:28.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He just said to come?

617
00:35:29.418 --> 00:35:31.212 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He said to bring cleaning supplies.

618
00:35:34.841 --> 00:35:36.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But... I forgot.

619
00:35:40.721 --> 00:35:42.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Drove over, let myself in.

620
00:35:43.432 --> 00:35:47.436 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Frank was in the living room.
He told me not to get upset.

621
00:35:47.520 --> 00:35:48.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Was he upset?

622
00:35:49.689 --> 00:35:50.731 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He was calm.

623
00:35:51.357 --> 00:35:54.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Okay. So Frank tells you
not to get upset...

624
00:35:56.195 --> 00:35:58.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He told me something bad had happened.

625
00:36:00.867 --> 00:36:04.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
My mind started racing, I was worried
something had happened to Benji.

626
00:36:07.915 --> 00:36:10.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Frank said, "He's fine,
but he's done something."

627
00:36:13.171 --> 00:36:14.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Benjamin did something?

628
00:36:17.800 --> 00:36:18.759 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yes.

629
00:36:21.012 --> 00:36:22.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I said, "What's he done?"

630
00:36:24.307 --> 00:36:27.393 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
He said he got mad at Beverly Jean.

631
00:36:37.570 --> 00:36:39.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Rose]<i> Frank said Benjamin hit her.</i>

632
00:36:41.657 --> 00:36:43.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I asked if she was okay.

633
00:36:48.331 --> 00:36:50.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Frank said,</i>
<i>"We got to help Benjamin out of this.</i>

634
00:36:51.042 --> 00:36:53.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We got to stick together
or he's going to get in trouble."

635
00:36:57.965 --> 00:36:59.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I asked where Benjamin was.</i>

636
00:37:00.718 --> 00:37:02.303 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>He said, "He's in the bathroom."</i>

637
00:37:03.888 --> 00:37:06.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I said, "I want to see him."</i>
<i>He said, "Okay.</i>

638
00:37:08.142 --> 00:37:10.144 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But Beverly Jean is in there too."

639
00:37:13.064 --> 00:37:14.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The door was open.

640
00:37:15.066 --> 00:37:17.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I saw Benji. He...

641
00:37:17.360 --> 00:37:20.071 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>He had his head in his hands,</i>
<i>he was crying.</i>

642
00:37:20.988 --> 00:37:23.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
There was blood everywhere.

643
00:37:24.075 --> 00:37:25.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Splashing.

644
00:37:27.161 --> 00:37:29.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>And then I see Beverly Jean</i>
<i>in the bathtub.</i>

645
00:37:31.457 --> 00:37:32.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Was she alive?

646
00:37:35.169 --> 00:37:36.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Dead.

647
00:37:38.005 --> 00:37:40.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
She had her top on, but no panties.

648
00:37:43.010 --> 00:37:45.888 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I said, "Benji, what have you done?"

649
00:37:47.807 --> 00:37:49.976 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He shook his head.
He didn't want to look at me.

650
00:37:50.601 --> 00:37:53.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Was she face up, face down?
-Face up.

651
00:37:53.354 --> 00:37:54.730 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Did you notice any wounds?

652
00:37:55.523 --> 00:37:57.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I couldn't tell, there was a lot of blood.

653
00:37:58.359 --> 00:37:59.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Then what happened?

654
00:37:59.986 --> 00:38:03.114 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Then Frank brought in a tarp,</i>
<i>spread it on the floor.</i>

655
00:38:03.614 --> 00:38:06.325 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Then he asked me</i>
<i>to go get cleaning supplies.</i>

656
00:38:07.076 --> 00:38:08.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
When I came back,
they had already rolled her up.

657
00:38:09.036 --> 00:38:12.123 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
So they took her out to Frank's truck
and drove off.

658
00:38:14.125 --> 00:38:16.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I washed out the tub
and cleaned up the bathroom.

659
00:38:17.128 --> 00:38:20.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I scrubbed the tiles, in the cracks,</i>

660
00:38:20.506 --> 00:38:22.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>the grouting, the window frame.</i>

661
00:38:23.175 --> 00:38:26.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I had to wash all the blood</i>
<i>down the sink and that seemed to...</i>

662
00:38:27.263 --> 00:38:28.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>It took forever...</i>

663
00:38:29.473 --> 00:38:31.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>trying to get it all to go down.</i>

664
00:38:33.102 --> 00:38:36.105 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[Tench] Did you see a weapon?
-There was a knife in the tub.

665
00:38:36.188 --> 00:38:37.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What'd you do with it?

666
00:38:38.858 --> 00:38:39.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Rose]<i> I rinsed it off.</i>

667
00:38:40.067 --> 00:38:43.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Took it to the kitchen,
washed it with dish soap.

668
00:38:43.612 --> 00:38:44.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Put it away.</i>

669
00:38:48.576 --> 00:38:49.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>And then I went home.</i>

670
00:38:50.077 --> 00:38:52.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Holden]<i> Did you see Frank or Benjamin</i>
<i>again that night?</i>

671
00:38:52.955 --> 00:38:53.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[Rose]<i> No.</i>

672
00:38:53.998 --> 00:38:55.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Frank came home early the next morning.</i>

673
00:38:58.961 --> 00:39:00.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why did you help them?

674
00:39:02.965 --> 00:39:04.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's just what I've always done.

675
00:39:07.345 --> 00:39:08.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Who killed her?

676
00:39:10.848 --> 00:39:12.058 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I don't know.

